name: SouthAfricanIdNumber_generateInvalidTest
description: Unit tests for generating invalid South African ID numbers.

test_cases.name: testGenerateInvalidSsn
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of an invalid South African ID number and verifies it is not valid.

test_cases.name: testGenerateInvalidSsnMultipleTimes
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of invalid South African ID numbers multiple times and verifies they are not valid.

test_cases.name: testGenerateInvalidSsnWithInvalidPattern
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of an invalid South African ID number and verifies it does not contain a specific invalid pattern.

test_cases.name: testGenerateInvalidSsnWithValidPattern
test_cases.description: Tests the generation of an invalid South African ID number and verifies it does not match a specific valid pattern.
